{"metadata":{"role":"symbol","title":"registerForPushNotificationsWith:","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)registerForPushNotificationsWith:","roleHeading":"Type Method","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"registerForPushNotificationsWith:","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"registerForPushNotificationsWith:"}]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Registers the device for push notifications with initial tags."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"registerForPushNotificationsWith:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSDictionary","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSDictionary","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"tags","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Dictionary of tag names and values to set during registration."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Supported value types: NSString, NSNumber, NSArray (for list tags).","type":"text"}]}],"name":"tags"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Combines push notification registration with tag assignment in a single operation."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This is more efficient than calling registerForPushNotifications and setTags separately,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"as tags are sent to the server along with the registration request.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Use this method when you have user attributes available at the time of registration,","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as during onboarding or after user authentication."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Example","level":2,"anchor":"Example","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Register with user attributes after sign-up:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["class SignUpCoordinator {","","    func completeSignUp(user: User, source: SignUpSource) {","        let registrationTags: [String: Any] = [","            \"user_type\": user.accountType.rawValue,","            \"signup_source\": source.analyticsValue,","            \"signup_date\": ISO8601DateFormatter().string(from: Date()),","            \"interests\": user.selectedInterests,","            \"language\": Locale.current.languageCode ?? \"en\",","            \"app_version\": Bundle.main.appVersion","        ]","","        Pushwoosh.configure.registerForPushNotifications(with: registrationTags)","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setUserId(user.id)","        Pushwoosh.configure.setEmail(user.email)","    }","}","","extension Bundle {","    var appVersion: String {","        infoDictionary?[\"CFBundleShortVersionString\"] as? String ?? \"unknown\"","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/registerforpushnotificationswith:"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/registerForPushNotificationsWith:"},"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/registerForPushNotificationsWith:":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/registerforpush